<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Portfólio</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center p-3" style="background-color: #252967;">
        <img src="" alt="logo" class="img-fluid" style="height: 50px;">

        <ul class="nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="#home"><strong>Home</strong></a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="#about-me"><strong>About me</strong></a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="#projects"><strong>Projects</strong></a>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <button class="btn btn-white" style="background-color: white; color: #252967;">Contact me!</button>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="home" class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between p-3">
            <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
            <img src="" alt="html logo" class="img-fluid mb-2">
            <img src="" alt="css logo" class="img-fluid mb-2">
            <img src="" alt="js logo" class="img-fluid mb-2">
            <img src="" alt="rails logo" class="img-fluid mb-2">
            <img src="" alt="github logo" class="img-fluid mb-2">
            <img src="" alt="me" class="img-fluid mb-2">
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="" style="color: #252967;">Hello! 
            I’m Cecilia, a WEB DEVELOPER based in Brazil!</h1>
            <p class="" style="color: #252967;">I have been working as a web developer since 2024.</p>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-white rounded mb-2" style="background-color: #252967; color: white;">Contact-me!</button>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <button class="btn btn-white rounded mx-1" style="background-color: #252967;">
                <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank">
                    <img src="path/to/github-icon.png" alt="GitHub">
                </a>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-white rounded mx-1" style="background-color: #252967;">
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" target="_blank">
                    <img src="path/to/linkedin-icon.png" alt="LinkedIn">
                </a>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-white rounded mx-1" style="background-color: #252967;">
                <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com">
                    <img src="path/to/email-icon.png" alt="Email">
                </a>
                </button>
            </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projects" class="bg-light py-5">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Projetos</h2>
            <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <%# @projects.each do |project| %>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 rounded">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title"><%#= project.title %></h3>
                        <p class="card-text"><%#= project.description %></p>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <%# end %>
            </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about-me" class="text-center py-5">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Sobre mim</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">My name is Cecilia, I am Brazilian and a web developer. I am very interested in technology and development, and I really love this field. I started my studies in 2023 when I began my degree in Software Engineering. After some time, in 2024, I started as an intern working in the field, and I have been working with it ever since!

            I want to continue my studies and gain a lot more knowledge in the world of technology, helping people, developing clean code software, and applying agile methodologies.

            My biggest dream is to travel the world, explore different cultures, and meet new people. This was one of the reasons I chose the field I work in today—because I believe that one day, I will be able to work from anywhere!

            Now that you know a little about me, check out my projects and skills in my portfolio!</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <img src="" alt="programming" class="rounded-circle mx-2" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
            <img src="" alt="park" class="rounded-circle mx-2" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
            <img src="" alt="travel" class="rounded-circle mx-2" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
            <img src="" alt="view" class="rounded-circle mx-2" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
            <img src="" alt="programming" class="rounded-circle mx-2" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer style="background-color: #252967; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
        <h2>Contact me!</h2>
        <p>If you liked my projects and need my skills, feel free to get in touch!</p>
        <button style="background-color: white; color: #252967; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 5px;">
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" target="_blank" style="color: #252967; text-decoration: none;">LinkedIn</a>
        </button>
        <button style="background-color: white; color: #252967; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 5px;">
            <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" style="color: #252967; text-decoration: none;">Email</a>
        </button>
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Cecília Camargo Prado</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>